need gsl gslcblas sqlite3 apophenia libraries in include path and library path for compilation and linking

Apophenia : http://apophenia.sourceforge.net/
gsl, gslcblas: http://www.gnu.org/software/gsl/
http://www.sqlite.org/download.html


when installing sqlite3:
./configure --prefix=/where/to/install/ --with-sqlite3=/parent/path/to/include/of/sqlite3headers/ --libdir=/path/to/lib/parent
then you need to modify MakeFile for the line LIBS= , add -lsqlite3
LIBS = -lmysqlclient -lgsl -lgslcblas -lm  -lsqlite3
then make install


run

modify make.sh to add -L/path/to/apophenia library in the g++ line and then

bash make.sh
